  "uuid": "9d6fcdbd9e53220d7e6e517a3e2bb47f",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Salesman",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>TECHLEAD TECHNOLOGY is a Singapore-based company dedicated to serving the semiconductor and high-tech industries. We specialize in providing high-quality semiconductor process equipment, material distribution services, and facility engineering solutions. With a focus on innovation, reliability, and customer satisfaction, TECHLEAD is committed to supporting our clients across the region with professional expertise and integrated solutions.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will drive business growth by managing client communications and negotiations, fostering strong customer relationships, and supporting sales initiatives. This role includes opportunities for overseas business travel and training to enhance your professional development.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead client communications and conduct business negotiations to secure and expand sales opportunities</li><li>Develop and maintain strong customer relationships to support long-term business growth</li><li>Support the company’s business development efforts by executing sales-related activities and initiatives</li><li>Participate in overseas business trips and training programs to enhance sales capabilities and market understanding</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in sales or business development, with a willingness to learn through available training</li><li>Ability to attend overseas training programs lasting up to one month</li><li>Willingness to undertake overseas business trips as required</li><li>Demonstrated service orientation and customer focus in previous roles</li><li>Effective communication and expression skills to engage clients and internal teams</li></ul>",
